'''Steve Niles''' (born [[June 21]], [[1960s#1965|1965]]) wrote the comic "[[Planet of the Dead]]" in ''[[Star Wars Tales 17]]''.

His most famous work is the comic [[Wikipedia:30 Days of Night|''30 Days of Night'']], which was illustrated by [[Ben Templesmith]], who also worked on [[Dark Journey (comic story)|a story]] in ''Star Wars Tales 17''.

